Anularea motorului.

1074
01:30:20.584 --> 01:30:21.895
Nu. nu. nu. nu. nu!

1075
01:30:21.919 --> 01:30:23.119
Motor peste-Nu!

1076
01:30:24.822 --> 01:30:25.822
La dracu '!

1077
01:30:28.692 --> 01:30:29.692
mami!

1078
