Nu. nu. nu. nu.

1082
01:31:41.331 --> 01:31:42.342
Nu. nu. Nick!

1083
01:31:42.366 --> 01:31:43.366
Nick!

1084
01:31:43.767 --> 01:31:44.767
Nick.

1085
